    "This is followed by pronoun resolution to make the relationship between two objects more explicit.",
    "Finally, plural nouns are processed.",
    "This involves copying noun instances when numeric modifiers are given.",
    "This textual scene graph is then mapped to images following [38].Cui et al. [72] also tackle text-based image retrieval.",
    "They present work that makes use of a GCN to provide cross-modal reasoning on visual and textual information."
